Supported OpenCart Versions:
================
2.x versions

Demo <a href=http://opencart.ostwork.com/index.php?route=checkout/cart>Front End</a>
Demo <a href=http://opencart.ostwork.com/admin/index.php?route=module/discount_on_1st_purchase>Back End</a> demo/demo

Discount on 1st purchase for opencart is a well thought out and excel­lently made mod­ule that allows to gives discount on first purchase. New Customer that have not purchase previously get this offer.


Features of Discount on 1st purchase extension
- Gives Discount on 1st purchase
- Discount shows only after login
- No Need of VQMOD
- Support Multi Store
- Support Multi Language

Special Features: Customize Discount on 1st purchase in following ways
	- Set Discount in %
	- Set Minimum total amount
	- Set Module Publish Date
	- Set Module End Date
	- Set Sort Order

Note: Set Sort Order to 2

